summary: In my research, I like to use art and scientific objects to ask and think through scientific and philosophical theories that pertain to the field of science and technology studies. I am also interested in questions that concern cities and ecologies, and how media, technology, and infrastructure come into play here.

During this conference, we want to conceptualize migration and borders as dialectically intertwined to create a profound understanding of them – and hopefully new insights.
